              Filing early maximizes your chances of receiving the most aid.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Federal Deadlines -->
      <section class="box-rounded mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-4">Federal FAFSA Deadlines</h2>

