          </div>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 p-5 rounded-lg border border-amber-200">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">‚è∞</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-800 mb-2">June 30, 2026</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-amber-900"><strong>Federal Deadline</strong></p>
            <p class="text-sm text-amber-700 mt-2">Last day to submit FAFSA for the 2025-26 year. State and school deadlines are much earlier.</p>
