              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Import tax information directly from the IRS to save time and reduce errors.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="text-brand-green-text font-bold">4.</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Know ALL Your Deadlines</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">You may have three different deadlines: federal, state, and institutional. Your college may have the earliest deadline of all.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="text-brand-green-text font-bold">5.</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Submit, Then Make Corrections</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">It's better to submit on time with estimates than to miss a deadline. You can make corrections after submitting.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
